  "title": "AI 进入「拼爹」的时代",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5OTAzMjc4MA==&mid=2650857327&idx=2&sn=67298249662a1d60ad091ef91dc4ce94",
  "date": "2026-01-12 03:25:00",
  "author": "创业邦",
  "siteName": "创业邦",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <div>\n    <div>\n     <div>\n      <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px 16px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5604395604395604\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2912\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/03KNO9Fib2w7f1V3nxcmqRMlhpK3Ghb0A0AQcSU134SkGo2KTNnZtfibyLPyXAdUrtLcuDI4YoEljdDx9tzYoKkA/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"546\" data-cropsely2=\"306\" data-backw=\"546\" data-backh=\"306\" data-imgfileid=\"503373554\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c90c8d01&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F03KNO9Fib2w7f1V3nxcmqRMlhpK3Ghb0A0AQcSU134SkGo2KTNnZtfibyLPyXAdUrtLcuDI4YoEljdDx9tzYoKkA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:14px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk7nxl601oq2\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">来源丨略大参考（ID：</span></span><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:14px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">hyzibenlu</span></span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:14px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk7nxl601oq2\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">）</span></span></p>\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:14px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk7nxl60187p\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">作者丨</span></span><span mpa-font-style=\"mk9107qr24hp\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:14px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;mpa-font-style&quot;:&quot;mk9107qr24hp&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-size: 15px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">杨知潮</span></span></span></p>\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:14px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk7nxl608wv\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">图源丨Midjourney</span></span></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mk9107qr1vbv\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">王晶曾说，过去的香港，每个拍电影的都是有“背景”的。因此演员和导演往往身不由己，电影生意的竞争也往往是背景的竞争。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk9107qr5ch\">AI生意越来越有这个意思。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk9107qr1a2p\">大家都带着背景和资源，这里是谷歌、微软、Meta、字节、腾讯、阿里交锋的修罗场。每一天，抖音用自己浩如烟海的流量铺天盖地推举豆包。谷歌用全公司的资源，在一系列APP里狂推自己的Gemini。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk9107qrjwb\">这种巨头之力，哪怕优秀如Manus、OpenAI也难以对抗。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk9107qr17yy\">2025年11月起，原本落后的谷歌迅速在性能和用户上追赶上了ChatGPT，尤其是在多模态领域，已经反超OpenAI在各种评测中位居第一。奥特曼直言，谷歌的崛起给OpenAI带来很大的压力。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk9107qr12ik\">曾经火遍全球的通用智能体Manus，也放弃了单打独斗，互联网巨头Meta选择将收购Manus。Kimi、DeepSeek这些红极一时的“当红炸子鸡”早已被豆包、元宝铺天盖地的流量压了下去。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk9107qr1jvt\">在这个拼爹的世界里，似乎只有超级巨头才有上桌的资格。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk9107qr9c7\">以小博大的故事在商业里十分常见。哪怕是腾讯、阿里、谷歌、苹果，也经常在某个领域输给创业公司。但在AI里，这种故事好像显得困难了许多。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.07777777777777778\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"900\" style=\"vertical-align:middle;max-width:100%;width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/03KNO9Fib2w5wrEGVRwwiaPQcjibpiahYT0zPEErlmM1icwAxnc0Bfu3icv2I49pcxADF7lYww8vNML5TkajhGu2m1NA/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-cropselx2=\"546\" data-cropsely2=\"271\" data-backw=\"546\" data-backh=\"42\" data-imgfileid=\"502705851\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d0e93a19&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F03KNO9Fib2w5wrEGVRwwiaPQcjibpiahYT0zPEErlmM1icwAxnc0Bfu3icv2I49pcxADF7lYww8vNML5TkajhGu2m1NA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></span></p>\n   <div>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><strong mpa-font-style=\"mk9107qradq\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:20px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk91cb0niid\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mk91cb15v73\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">看能力，更看资源</span></span></strong></p>\n   </div>\n   <div>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mk9107qr1gbr\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">娱乐圈里有一种说法，艺人只要给足饱和式的曝光，都能红。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk9107qrpne\">这也是眼下AI领域的现状。ChatGPT是ChatBot的发明者，相当于苹果发明了现代智能手机，无论是技术，还是品牌，都是真正的遥遥领先。但当超级巨头谷歌发力，ChatGPT很快感受到了压力。Gemini在多项机构评测中反超GPT，奥特曼在内部信中发出警告：公司的技术领先优势正在缩小，并预计外界氛围将在一段时间内“相当艰难”。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk9107qr1shj\">国内市场，豆包早已取代Kimi成为月活第一的LLM产品。以搭载DeepSeek为卖点的元宝用户数据也早已反超DeepSeek，成为了DeepSeek崛起的流量受益者。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk9107qr1g1x\">它们为什么如此强势，逆袭领先者？答案当然是因为有谷歌、字节跳动这些大厂在背后提供资源。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong mpa-font-style=\"mk9107qr1kp7\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">其实明星AI创业公司背后都有大企业和大资本的投资，账上也有很多钱，也有很多资源。但背靠巨头带来的生态优势，创业公司们真的没法复刻。</span></strong></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk9107qrk3s\">比如谷歌直接把Gemini植入安卓，作为默认的手机助手。谷歌还有排名第一的浏览器Chrome，Gmail，微软的Copilot也直接融入Office套件。这种与常用APP绑定的方式，用户不用也得用——而且为什么不用呢？深度集成入常用APP的AI，体验是非常丝滑的。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk9107qrj91\">金山软件和微软一样，直接把AI融进WPS里。腾讯也直接把元宝塞进微信里，用户无需下载任何APP就能在微信聊天框里体验到LLM。哪怕是AI落脚点相对少的阿里和蚂蚁，也有支付宝、夸克这样的优质入口。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mk9107qrpse\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">这样的做法OpenAI、Manus、Kimi们要如何模仿？</span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">难道为了与大厂竞争，还要自己做一个手机操作系统或者微信？</span></strong></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk9107qrgrq\">有些生意，是自力更生，创业公司挑战巨头虽然困难，但也有机会。比如米哈游靠着几部爆款游戏，迅速在二次元游戏领域里成为老大，网易和腾讯资源再多，也没能阻止米哈游的崛起。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong mpa-font-style=\"mk9107qrbat\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">但有些生意，对外界的依附太重。AI应用恰恰是这种生意。</span></strong></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk9107qr1i\">第一，当然是因为它资产太重，互联网产品最大的成本往往是买流量，但AI背后可能是数千亿美元的固定资产，居民楼创业玩不转。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong mpa-font-style=\"mk9107qr1fpn\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">第二，更重要的是，它的使用场景，与生态的绑定太深，太需要与其他产品的联动。</span></strong></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk9107qr10mr\">Manus就是个很好的例子：它的功能当然强大，但在个人用户端完全没法独立干活，它需要“调用”其他网页，依赖浏览器和浏览器中的数据。比如订一张机票，需要账号授权、支付授权——这些东西都掌握在谷歌、苹果、微信这种巨头手里。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk9107qr1lcv\">Manus干的是系统级的活，却完全没有系统级的权限。相当于普通孩子学了一门“千万资产理财课”，但他家却没有千万资产。当谷歌这种浏览器和手机操作系统的拥有者亲自下场，留给独立智能体的空间就会越来越狭小。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk9107qr1m4b\">AI搜索也感受到了这种压力。毕竟在这个时代，搜索早不是什么独立的APP了，iPhone里的搜索框，是由苹果公司控制的。Perplexity再好用，它也不是苹果的默认搜索引擎——谷歌一年付200亿美元获得了这个身份。在国内，搜索框则由百度、微信、手机厂商把持，他们很难把搜索框交给AI创业公司。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk9107qrjy6\">即便他们利用技术优势，暂时在大厂的竞争压力中获得一定份额，他们还要面临第二个难题：变现。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.07777777777777778\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"900\" style=\"vertical-align:middle;max-width:100%;width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/03KNO9Fib2w5wrEGVRwwiaPQcjibpiahYT0zSsWdBUSJRaL8xxhHssPefRrhSRCKFFTvyO0oNl4HVrDTxA2PCXqv1g/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-cropselx2=\"546\" data-cropsely2=\"42\" data-backw=\"546\" data-backh=\"42\" data-imgfileid=\"502705850\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9f561975&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F03KNO9Fib2w5wrEGVRwwiaPQcjibpiahYT0zSsWdBUSJRaL8xxhHssPefRrhSRCKFFTvyO0oNl4HVrDTxA2PCXqv1g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></span></p>\n   <div>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><strong mpa-font-style=\"mk9107qru9p\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:20px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk91csa61qgz\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mk91csamsrl\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">AI的变现，也得拼爹</span></span></strong></p>\n   </div>\n   <div>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mk9107qrqk9\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">富贵人家，总是更容易收回教育孩子的成本。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk9107qr10ds\">他们送孩子去读个水硕，可以凭借家庭关系安排进国际银行，或者进入家族企业担当要职。但穷人家送孩子去国外读一年硕士，毕业却可能会因为学历含金量不高找不到工作。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk9107qrma9\">视角切到AI的变现身上，也没什么不同，同样的一个技术，小公司持有难以变现，大公司就能以不同的方式收到钱。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk9107qr22eu\">比如在OpenAI还在陷入亏损难题的时候，微软就通过把GPT服务打包进自家云服务实现了业绩的大幅度增长。OpenAI Service已经成了微软Azure的王牌产品之一，毕竟客户们本来就购买了微软的云服务，再买点AI服务，属于捆绑销售。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk9107qryxc\">更不用说Copilot和Office（Microsoft 365）的联动，微软把AI工具加入到办公套件里，上调订阅费——不接受？那就别用Office。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk9107qr14ok\">这也是微软过去十年重要的增长来源。每当新技术、新变革、新功能出现时，他们就可以对订阅服务涨价。当然这种涨价是双赢的，客户也收获了便利和价值。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk9107qr8r8\">在C端，从Gemini和OpenAI的会员中，也可以看到捆绑销售能力的差距：同样是卖20美元，谷歌就可以打包把谷歌One（安卓版本的iCloud）一并打包售卖，AI之外，用户还能获得Gmail、相册里的存储空间。这是非常具备吸引力的捆绑销售方案，毕竟哪怕不用AI，用户也需要邮件和存照片。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk9107qr1ujv\">不难想象，如果Manus属于谷歌这样的巨头，也许它也会把Manus的订阅服务加进这个20美元套餐里，Manus的变现就会更加顺滑。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div>\n    <p style=\"margin:0px 16px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-ratio=\"0.49722222222222223\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align:middle;max-width:100%;width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;\" data-backw=\"546\" data-backh=\"271\" data-imgfileid=\"110062727\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9ec6da83&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FPAHrFsX2icOVlEflpotLEPibzkeUwyNcJicvEu0UyDY7seAR8YgzhftNQhtWOqzhlpHOYicQ0mbjz4G6BcJdicKsBsA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%23imgIndex%3D1\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div>\n    <p style=\"margin:0px 16px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-ratio=\"0.55\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align:middle;max-width:100%;width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;\" data-backw=\"546\" data-backh=\"300\" data-imgfileid=\"110062728\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a12e6bbe&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FPAHrFsX2icOVlEflpotLEPibzkeUwyNcJicf7L9WfNfY1IjgD5aDdrp5oHrCxz1bmeY9ra2gXGlYyPxLRn3670Hxw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%23imgIndex%3D2\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mk9107qrwvn\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">而OpenAI的订阅几乎只有ChatGPT，哪怕Sora、Codex等新产品，也是靠OpenAI自己做的。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk9107qr1bke\">豆包的变现花样更加丰富。豆包的回答会把流量引入短视频——之后的商业模式就可以和抖音一样了，在视频中间插入广告就好。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk9107qr60\">豆包还上线了直接的Chat广告，对话框的回答可以直达抖音生态内部的本地生活等服务。比如在豆包里问附近的好餐馆，豆包会直接给出团购链接。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div>\n    <p style=\"margin:0px 16px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-ratio=\"1.3541666666666667\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1056\" style=\"vertical-align:middle;max-width:100%;width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;\" data-backw=\"546\" data-backh=\"739\" data-imgfileid=\"110062730\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e1d2c1c6&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FPAHrFsX2icOVlEflpotLEPibzkeUwyNcJicS3G5J0SpVibjJgeichokIg2JBuBDpCW85IdC54YtrabC5zFkN9hFvxiaA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg%23imgIndex%3D3\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mk91dmnr20qr\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:12px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk91dmnb21aj\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">点击链接，就能直达餐馆的抖音团购界面</span></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mk9107qr1mq2\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">这种商业模式Kimi们很难学习，毕竟创业公司可没有抖音那么多短视频储备，也没有发达的本地生活服务或者电商的供应链。它只能向外去卖流量，但眼下的AI行业格局来看，大多数交易平台并不愿意把入口交给其他AI工具，即便愿意，变现的转化率也不如生态内那样高。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mk9107qr20vr\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">如果没有这些变现花样，那么AI的</span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">商业模式和老干妈辣酱差不多——一手交钱，一手交货。也就是在B端卖Token，C端卖订阅。</span></strong></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk9107qrf29\">但这个模式太卷了：客户只在乎多少钱买到多少Token，难以像微软的云服务一样溢价。个人用户的订阅费价格被用户习惯和行业共识限制：要么20美元，要么10-30人民币。这是多个行业与用户长期博弈出来的价格，是用户订阅习惯的平衡点，大多数行业的订阅会员，最后都会回归到这个数字附近。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div>\n    <p style=\"margin:0px 16px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-ratio=\"0.7787037037037037\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align:middle;max-width:100%;width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;\" data-backw=\"546\" data-backh=\"425\" data-imgfileid=\"110062729\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f6396000&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FPAHrFsX2icOVlEflpotLEPibzkeUwyNcJicBaVv4JLat4gD6FDcD3icyO7NhLqA4hIB6C4vm58P0zpPepB140AdJgA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg%23imgIndex%3D4\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:12px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk91eh0n1zw3\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mk91eh1311wy\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">MiniMax国内产品“星野”的订阅费用。事实上，国内大多数会员的网络订阅会员的价格都在这个数字附近，谁想卖更贵都很困难</span></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mk9107qre24\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">最近递交招股书的智普AI和MiniMax，亏损数据都十分严重——创业公司，亏损当然很正常，但它们的亏损呈现逐年扩大趋势，暂时看不到盈利预期在哪里。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk9107qr1xtr\">事实上，这二者的亏损被广泛讨论并不是因为它们的亏损尤为突出，只是因为它们递交了招股书，在那些没有递交招股书的AI企业中，还藏着更为广泛、普遍的亏损。哪怕是已经有7亿用户的OpenAI也不例外。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk9107qr1p1v\">而这个问题，创业公司自己解决起来异常困难，最终很可能需要仰仗大厂的力量。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.07777777777777778\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"900\" style=\"vertical-align:middle;max-width:100%;width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/03KNO9Fib2w5wrEGVRwwiaPQcjibpiahYT0zotCTF2kebByIao1mukeoCXNY3JU0WuJBsy2jtgbt4REff8WQwWR4oQ/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-cropselx2=\"546\" data-cropsely2=\"42\" data-backw=\"546\" data-backh=\"42\" data-imgfileid=\"502705852\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b2401e1e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F03KNO9Fib2w5wrEGVRwwiaPQcjibpiahYT0zotCTF2kebByIao1mukeoCXNY3JU0WuJBsy2jtgbt4REff8WQwWR4oQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></span></p>\n   <div>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><strong mpa-font-style=\"mk9107qr1nkp\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:20px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk91f98wkgu\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mk91f99euw3\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">小蝌蚪找爸爸</span></span></strong></p>\n   </div>\n   <div>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mk9107qr14wc\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">在这个“拼爹”的世界里，单打独斗似乎很难出头。当出价合理，卖身给巨头，也是不错的选择。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk9107qr20e0\">Meta接连宣布收购Scale和Manus，苹果也被爆出考虑收购Perlexity。一旦被收购，情况就完全不同了。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk9107qr217n\">以Manus为例，它过去想调用一些功能，要看其他公司给不给权限，还要面临巨头自研智能体的竞争风险。但一旦属于Meta，Manus就可以直接在WhatsAPP、INS、Messenger、Facebook里获得原生级别的权限，随意调用各种聊天、购物的功能。更不用说Meta还有AI硬件的布局，如果与AR眼镜结合，Manus就能直接获取SIRI级别的权限。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk9107qr1bwt\">这类AI应用公司，被大厂收购的好处实在是显而易见。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk9107qrrch\">当然，如果自己能成为大厂，谁愿意依附大厂呢？</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk9107qr103k\">OpenAI就不愿意。OpenAI原本是有巨头靠山的，微软是它的最大的单一机构股东。但可惜，由于特殊的架构，微软并没有获得OpenAI的控制权。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk9107qrrth\">微软管不了OpenAI，自然就不拿它当“亲儿子”，不但自己有自己的AI产品，还训练自己的模型。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk9107qr1xji\">OpenAI也不想给谁做子公司，作为LLM的最大开创者，它只想自己成为超级大厂。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk9107qr41s\">明明微软有现成的Edge浏览器，但OpenAI还是自己想做浏览器Atlas，明明微软是最大的云服务商，自己找合作伙伴建立算力能力，还与谷歌合作购买GCP服务。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk9107qr2au\">显然，OpenAI希望成为美股七姐妹那样真正的超级巨头。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk9107qrx64\">这条路在互联网时代是被验证过的，每当行业出现大的变革，总会出现创业公司的崛起，用灵活性打得巨头节节败退，甚至最终自己成为巨头。比如字节跳动在BAT三家统治的互联网里，硬是从居民楼里杀出一条血路，成为互联网的新一极。还有拼多多、米哈游这种在与腾讯和阿里的竞争中胜利，成为细分领域头部的公司。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk9107qr105\">毕竟行业的红利时期总是充满变革，方向、创意、技术、灵活性才是最重要的。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk9107qrk0m\">但这条路在AI领域显得难了太多，三年过去，创业公司的灵活性优势和先发优势不断被大厂的体量碾压，超级巨头的优势愈发明显。巨头对各种系统级的入口掌握权限，起到的作用太大了。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk9107qr1bcg\">如果说AI故事的第一章叫作「技术的革命」，那么第二章的主题，看起来越来越像「权力的游戏」。</span></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "文章指出当前 AI 领域竞争已演变为巨头“拼爹”，创业公司因资源、生态、变现劣势难以独立突围，AI 行业正从技术竞赛走向权力博弈。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "文章指出当前 AI 领域竞争已演变为巨头“拼爹”，创业公司因资源、生态、变现劣势难以独立突围，AI 行业正从技术竞赛走向权力博弈。",
  "summary": "文章深入探讨了当前 AI 领域中“拼爹”现象的普遍性，认为 AI 生意的竞争已从纯粹的技术较量转向巨头之间的资源和生态系统竞争。通过对比 Google、微软、字节跳动等巨头与 OpenAI、Manus、Kimi 等创业公司的发展路径和困境，文章指出巨头凭借其流量入口、生态整合能力（如操作系统、浏览器、常用应用绑定）以及强大的变现能力，在用户获取和商业模式上占据压倒性优势。创业公司即使技术领先，也因资产过重、场景深度绑定以及变现渠道受限而面临巨大挑战。最终文章总结，AI 领域的第一章是“技术革命”，第二章则逐渐演变为“权力的游戏”，多数创业公司或将被巨头收购，或沦为巨头生态的一部分。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "AI 领域竞争从技术主导转向资源和生态决定。",
      "explanation": "巨头企业通过整合自身庞大的用户基础、流量入口和生态系统，对 AI 产品进行饱和式推广和深度绑定，使得技术优秀的创业公司难以匹敌。"
    },
    {
      "point": "巨头生态优势使得 AI 应用难以独立发展。",
      "explanation": "AI 应用对外部依附性强，需要操作系统、浏览器、常用 APP 等系统级权限和数据支持，这正是谷歌、微软、字节等巨头独有的优势，创业公司难以复制。"
    },
    {
      "point": "AI 创业公司面临巨大的变现困境。",
      "explanation": "相比巨头能将 AI 服务打包进云服务、办公套件或现有生态（如短视频、本地生活）进行捆绑销售，创业公司仅依靠售卖 Token 或订阅难以盈利，普遍面临严重亏损。"
    },
    {
      "point": "多数 AI 创业公司最终可能被巨头收购。",
      "explanation": "在“拼爹”的背景下，创业公司单打独斗难以生存，被有实力的巨头收购，融入其生态，成为获取原生权限和商业化路径的更优选择。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "AI 生意越来越有这个意思。大家都带着背景和资源，这里是谷歌、微软、Meta、字节、腾讯、阿里交锋的修罗场。",
    "背靠巨头带来的生态优势，创业公司们真的没法复刻。难道为了与大厂竞争，还要自己做一个手机操作系统或者微信？",
    "AI 应用恰恰是这种生意：第一，因为它资产太重，互联网产品最大的成本往往是买流量，但 AI 背后可能是数千亿美元的固定资产，居民楼创业玩不转。 第二，更重要的是，它的使用场景，与生态的绑定太深，太需要与其他产品的联动。",
    "同样的一个技术，小公司持有难以变现，大公司就能以不同的方式收到钱。",
    "AI 故事的第一章叫作「技术的革命」，那么第二章的主题，看起来越来越像「权力的游戏」。"
